HB 1163 Original 2026 Regular Session Chance Henry
Abstract: Provides relative to the sale of fireworks.
Present law provides that permissible items of fireworks, enumerated in present law, may
be sold at retail only from noon June 16th through midnight July 5th and noon Dec. 15th
through midnight Jan. 1st of each calendar year.
